WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
[M-Fire Suppression logo with flame effect animation.]

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
[Industrial bucket labeled "AF-31 Fire Inhibitor" shown on an active construction site with exposed wood framing.]

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:30.000
[Worker in safety gear sprays AF-31 onto wood framing using a compression sprayer, coating the lumber evenly.]

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:45.000
[Aerial drone footage of a large multi-story residential construction complex with extensive wood framing visible across multiple buildings.]
